OPTOMA CORP (3565)  said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 9.70% to NT$338,852,000 from NT$375,240,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            338,852          375,240    
YOY%              -9.70%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,127,926        2,034,220   
YOY%              4.61%  
=================================================================
 